platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Découvrez la musique avec des animations et des mini-jeux.
Learn about musical concepts through animations, voice acting and mini games.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 走进有形有声的卡通音乐世界
音感とリズムを身につけよう

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: You’re never too young to start learning about harmony and rhythm. Easy Music teaches musical concepts through charming animations, great voice acting, and entertaining mini games. There are memory challenges, rhythm games, and freeform stages where nearly everything is a pleasure to tap on—from dancing flamingos to singing squirrels and drum-kit mushrooms. Little ones will love experimenting with the oodles of unique sound effects, and when they’re ready they can record their creations.
